Dialogs.Text: Thomas B: Oh, finally! There she is!
LostDecipher2: There you are, i thought you logged out for a second.
LostDecipher2: Wait, no, i could've check the chat log and...
LostDecipher2: Forget it, the thing is that i found you!
MsMaki95: Were you... Looking for me?
LostDecipher2: ...? Well, yeah, what kind of question is that? You said you were going to show me something. But you were so fast and this place is kind of confusing!
MsMaki95: Oh... Ah, yeah, sorry, emotion kinda took me and... I forgot you were new here.
MsMaki95: Still, really good finding your way here on your own.
LostDecipher2: What can i say? I'm good at figuring things out.
MsMaki95: Oh, speaking of which, you know what this is?
LostDecipher2: ...Well, no, but it seems glitched.
LostDecipher2: But i can see... A name or two.
MsMaki95: We are trying to fix it, i think it was supposed to be a mural, but none of the tools i used seem to work with it.
LostDecipher2: So, the bugged textures can't be overwritten by new information.
MsMaki95: Maybe, but we don't want the information to be lost, so i'm not touching this much.
LostDecipher2: And the archives can't be downloaded
MsMaki95: It doesn't seem like it...
